"Night Garden Bigfoot"
South Florida Compendium
2021
6000 x 5000 px, JPEG

/// (Captured at Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden)

The SoFLa Compendium uses glitch photogrammetry to catalog various objects of power, auratic spaces, and angelic entities throughout Miami and Broward County during Miami Art Week 2021.

Works are a collaboration with the artist's 15-year-old brother Joshua, who created the 3D scans.
